title: 223: Carson Wentz for MVP?
itunes:title: 223: Carson Wentz for MVP?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the Eagles big win over the Redskins on Monday Night Football (00:14). The guys also take a big picture look at the NFC East (8:56) before they look back on the 2016 NFL Draft class (10:12). DJ and Bucky are also joined by one of the top tight end prospects in the 2018 class, South Dakota State's Dallas Goedert (14:59).
